    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEMO VERSION</h2>This demo features two playable characters and the first chapter of the story. Enjoy!<br><br>Build powerful combos in this two-character roguelike deckbuilder. Craft a deck as you progress through adventures and follow an immersive storyline told using hand drawn comics!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/bca6f8684c32a72d9c8863921c0eb3c6.poster.avif?t=1728786426\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/bca6f8684c32a72d9c8863921c0eb3c6.webm?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/bca6f8684c32a72d9c8863921c0eb3c6.mp4?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game features a unique mana system that elevates your decision-making to the next level. When one character plays a card, the other character gets one mana. However, mana comes in different colors! Play the right cards in order to unlock stronger ones in your hand!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/4ec9b84ca7c5d32d60c4dab40e18d567.poster.avif?t=1728786426\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/4ec9b84ca7c5d32d60c4dab40e18d567.webm?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/4ec9b84ca7c5d32d60c4dab40e18d567.mp4?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore a unique experience every time you embark on a run. Choose any two characters to form a team, unlocking new potentials from each!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/c335997dfbf41c982fb30b933835f51c.poster.avif?t=1728786426\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/c335997dfbf41c982fb30b933835f51c.webm?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/c335997dfbf41c982fb30b933835f51c.mp4?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join our heroes in their journey through a story told using fully colored comics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/9ffc0fa374f8eb560e53e4b00f8292fa.poster.avif?t=1728786426\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/9ffc0fa374f8eb560e53e4b00f8292fa.webm?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163600/extras/9ffc0fa374f8eb560e53e4b00f8292fa.mp4?t=1728786426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
